name: 500 Phantom Galaxies Starlings
description:
Phantom Galaxies’ Starling is a premium in-game currency. Its in-game uses include buying M-Cubes for Manufacturing gear and weapons, U-Cubes for Upgrading gear and weapons, and F-Cubes for Starfighter Fusion, and more.

Phantom Galaxies base game required. Phantom Galaxies Starlings can only be used in Phantom Galaxies.
